Annotation.P: This system simulates NARMA-L2 control of a magnet suspended by an electromagnet.
Double-click on the NARMA-L2 Controller block to train the neural network controller and plant model.
For more information on what the controller does, look under the mask of the NARMA-L2 Controller block.

Object.P: NARMA-L2 Controller. You first train a neural network model of the plant to be controlled. The controller is a rearrangement of the trained plant model. Double-click the NARMA-L2 Controller block to begin the plant training.

Annotation.P: NARMA-L2 Control of a Magnet Levitation System (Double click on the "?" for more info)
To start and stop the simulation, use the "Start/Stop" selection in the "Simulation" pull-down menu
